Summary:        A network performance benchmark tool.
Name:           iperf
Version:        3.12
Release:        1%{?dist}
License:        BSD
URL:            https://github.com/esnet/iperf
Group:          Applications/System
Vendor:         VMware, Inc.
Distribution:   Photon
#Source download URL: https://github.com/esnet/iperf/archive/3.8.1.tar.gz
